&reftitle.description;
public boolZipArchive::addFile stringfilepath stringentryname"" intstart0 intlength0 intflagsZipArchive::FL_OVERWRITE
Adds a file to a ZIP archive from a given path.
&zip.filename.separator;

  &reftitle.examples;


     This example opens a ZIP file archive
     test.zip and add
     the file /path/to/index.txt.
     as newname.txt.


     Open and add


<?php
$zip = new ZipArchive;
if ($zip->open('test.zip') === TRUE) {
    $zip->addFile('/path/to/index.txt', 'newname.txt');
    $zip->close();
    echo 'ok';
} else {
    echo 'failed';
}
?>
